            "id": 6398278,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 新思科技(SNPS-US)大跌5.04%，報381.71美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)截至台北時間28日02:44股價下跌20.24美元，報381.71美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量1,545,358（股），盤中最高價401.54美元、最低價381.71美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-1.53%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-1.47%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-1.92%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.69%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>新思科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SNPS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SNPS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SNPS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-6.14%</li> <li>近 1 月：-5.65%</li> <li>近 3 月：-15.76%</li> <li>近 6 月：-17.59%</li> <li>今年以來：-14.43%</li></ul></section></main>",
